column5: Got into some splake on an inland lake up north, never fished them before, caught a couple dozen on the trip.    Uploaded with ImageShack.us      A little fall muskie action too.
Those splake are gorgeous (and the musky aint bad either  )
That's a helluva fall report...sweet splake.  How'd they taste?
Sweet ski looks like a good trip
Nice ski! He must be filling up on splake haha
So thats what them splake look like ... not too far from me brookies.  Nice report.  And yes how did they taste?
